 "bio": "Fern Brady is a Scottish stand-up comedian, podcaster and writer from Bathgate, West Lothian, known for blunt, deadpan material. She reached the final of So You Think Youre Funny in 2011 and became the first Scottish woman to perform on Live at the Apollo. Her memoir Strong Female Character, about her late autism diagnosis, was a bestseller, and her stand-up specials include Power and Chaos and the Netflix release Autistic Bikini Queen.",
